        map.put("Market Value", new ArrayList<>(Arrays.asList("Market value or OMV (Open Market Valuation) is the price at which an asset would trade in a competitive auction setting. Market value is often used interchangeably with open market value, fair value or fair market value, although these terms have distinct definitions in different standards, and differ in some circumstances.","Selling a stock to a good friend at a discount of 35% is a market price?", "Yes", "Depends", "Probably not", "Impossible to know", "C")));
